Winter Olympics 1992:
   Games Stats: Speed Skating
-- Number of records Eric Heiden set at the 1980 games: 6
(5 Olympic records and 1 world record).
                                                                                                       

   -- Heiden's thigh and waist measurements at the 1980
games: 29 inches and 32 inches, respectively.
                                                                                                       

   -- Number of silver medals awarded in the women's
500-meter race in 1968: 3 (Americans Dianne Holum, Jennifer
Fish and Mary Meyers tied for second place).
                                                                                                       

